<script>
  window['_cpga'] = window['_cpga'] || {};
  _cpga.playedVideos = {};

  _cpga.videoIsFirstPlay = function (playerType, videoIdentifier) {
    return (typeof _cpga.playedVideos[playerType] === 'undefined' || _cpga.playedVideos[playerType][videoIdentifier] === -1);
  };

  _cpga.getVideoTimeViewed = function (playerType, videoIdentifier) {
    if (_cpga.playedVideos[playerType] && _cpga.playedVideos[playerType][videoIdentifier]) {
      return Math.round((Date.now() - _cpga.playedVideos[playerType][videoIdentifier]) / 1000);
    } else {
      return undefined;
    }
  };

  _cpga.resetVideoTimeViewed = function (playerType, videoIdentifier) {
    if (typeof _cpga.playedVideos[playerType] === 'undefined') {
      _cpga.playedVideos[playerType] = {};
    }

    _cpga.playedVideos[playerType][videoIdentifier] = Date.now();
  };
</script>

<script>
"use strict";

/**
  * Description - HTML5 Video Tracking, only works on browsers that support HTML5
  * Version - 1.0
*/
try {
	var lastP;
	var intervalId;
	var title;
	var html5Video;
	var i;

	(function () {
		var onProgress = function onProgress(e, title) {
			//console.log("in progress");
			intervalId = setInterval(function () {
				var duration = e.target.duration;
				var position = e.target.currentTime;
				var t = duration - position <= 1.5 ? 1 : (Math.floor(position / duration * 4) / 4).toFixed(2);
				if (!lastP[title] || t > lastP[title]) {
					lastP[title] = t;
					dataLayer.push({
						event: "e_video",
						videoAction: t * 100 + "% viewed",
						videoLabel: title,
						videoTimeViewed: _cpga.getVideoTimeViewed('html5', title)
					});
					_cpga.resetVideoTimeViewed('html5', title);
				}
			}, 200);
		};

		lastP = [];
		title = "";
		html5Video = document.getElementsByTagName("video");

		for (i = 0; i < html5Video.length; ++i) {
			title = html5Video[i].getElementsByTagName("source")[0].src;
			html5Video[i].onplay = function (e) {
				//console.log("in play");
				var pushObj = {
					event: "e_video",
					videoAction: "play",
					videoLabel: title
				};

				if (_cpga.videoIsFirstPlay('html5', title)) {
					pushObj.videoStart = 1;
					pushObj.videoDuration = e.target.duration;
				}

				dataLayer.push(pushObj);
				_cpga.resetVideoTimeViewed('html5', title);
				onProgress(e, title);
			};
			html5Video[i].onpause = function () {
				//console.log("in pause");
				dataLayer.push({
					event: "e_video",
					videoAction: "pause",
					videoLabel: title,
					videoTimeViewed: _cpga.getVideoTimeViewed('html5', title)
				});
				clearInterval(intervalId);
			};

			html5Video[i].onended = function () {
				clearInterval(intervalId);
			};
		}
	})();
} catch (ex) {}
</script>
